                        </div>

                        <div class="card-body pt-7">
                            <p>
                                <ul>
                                    <h5>
                                        <li>Subscribers must be below 50 years</li>
                                        <li>Must request to be moved to this Fund</li>
                                        <li>Only subscribers in Fund II can move to Fund I</li>
                                        <li>Will be more aggressive in terms of asset allocation</li>
                                        <li>More risky assets included and thus, more target returns </li>
                                        <li>Minimum of 20% of assets will be invested in variable income assets</li>
                                        <li>Maximum of 70% of assets can be invested in variable income assets.</li>
                                    </h5></ul>
                            </p>


                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card col-lg-3 ">
