                                        <li>Will be more conservative in terms of asset allocation</li>
                                        <li>Minimum of 0% of assets will be invested in variable assets</li>
                                        <li>Maximum of 10% of assets can be invested in variable assets</li>
                                        <li>Returns will be similar to the existing Retiree Fund’s</li>
                                    </h5>
                                         </ul>
                            </p>


